  DISEASES & MEDICINE
============================================================

Disease:     Ebola
Type:        Viral
Pathogen:    Ebola virus
Transmission:Bodily fluids contact
Symptoms:    Fever, bleeding, organ failure
Treatment:   Monoclonal antibodies, supportive
Deaths/yr:   0.001M
Vaccine:     Yes (Ervebo for Zaire strain)
Discovered:  1976

Disease:     Smallpox
Type:        Viral
Pathogen:    Variola
Transmission:Respiratory, contact
Symptoms:    Pockmarks, fever
Treatment:   Eradicated (1980)
Deaths/yr:   EradicatedM
Vaccine:     Yes
Discovered:  Antiquity

Disease:     Cholera
Type:        Bacterial
Pathogen:    Vibrio cholerae
Transmission:Contaminated water
Symptoms:    Profuse watery diarrhea, vomiting
Treatment:   Oral rehydration, antibiotics
Deaths/yr:   0.095M
Vaccine:     Yes
Discovered:  1854

